"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-07-17-Exclusive-Allman-wants-to-defend-her-Olympic-discus-title-in-Paris--1vj45OB4uXe-p.html\", \"text\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use. You can change your cookie settings through your browser.  Sports Scene  Copied  Tokyo Olympics women's discus throw gold medalist Valarie Allman of the United States recently had an exclusive interview with CGTN Sports Scene. The 29-year-old told Sports Scene reporter Zhu Mandan she is looking to defend her title in the event while enjoying her second Olympics journey.  (Cover: Valarie Allman of the United States celebrates with her silver medal during a studio photo session after the women's discus throw final at the World Athletics Championships in Budapest, Hungary, August 23, 2023. /CFP)  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\"}"